survey_response.review_text: Great doctors with great amenities.. I was in severe pain since last many days due to swelling in my lower last tooth but Dr. Shines removed that extra tissue so carefully with laser.. I didn't get any stitches in fact..  I am so grateful that I met him..  Thanks..

I visited dentlife and my experience was very good. All the doctors are very good and kind. They explained me everything before doing the procedure. Dr.vidhi did all my root canals and tooth color fillings. Dr.shivesh and Dr. Nidhi did my implant in lower teeth which was all painless. Thank you.

Dr.shivesh is such a genuine doctor. Evrybody told me to get my tooth removed but he recommended me that i should save my tooth. Using an advanced procedure using laser he increased my tooth length and gave me a cap over it after doing my RCT.thanks to him

Dr.Shivesh did my cleaning and polishing followed by laser disinfection of my gums. all my pain is gone now. i am so thankful to him. god bless u.
